summary: This document is a customer experience survey notification from Fifth Third Bank regarding their mortgage services. It expresses appreciation for the customer's choice of Fifth Third Bank and encourages participation in a survey conducted by ath Power Consulting to improve service levels. The document emphasizes the bank's commitment to customer service and privacy.
keyFacts: The document is a customer experience survey notification from Fifth Third Bank.
The survey is conducted by ath Power Consulting.
Fifth Third Bank assures customers that their personal information will not be shared with ath Power Consulting.
The document emphasizes Fifth Third Bank's commitment to customer service.
